    <item>
      <title>抢劫，超越模因股票，现在想成为您的银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/robinhood-moving-beyond-meme-stocks-now-wants-to-be-your-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Robinhood Markets Inc.已经超越了其模因股票天数，成为所有条纹零售投资者的首选贸易平台 - 加密狂热者，新手金融家和先进的投机者。现在，它将它更进一步：它也想成为您的银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/robinhood-moving-beyond-meme-stocks-now-wants-to-be-your-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
